messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Oh, it's 12. Question 12. Eight point zero one two.
Go ahead. What seems to be the problem?
We got a call. We're evacuating right now.
What's your location?
Ampy.
Copy. I just received information about a possible shooting at the high school cafeteria.
Say that again?
A possible shooting at the high school cafeteria. Can you check on that?
You're on the fight right now.
Alright, it's an active shooter situation for now.
Marysville, shut the cafeteria until verification.
Copy. Multiple units are en route.
We've got probably four down.
Copy, four down, one confirmed. Do we have casualties?
One confirmed down, possibly more.
We have multiple units in county, all are responding.
I need immediate aid here, I have two that are still breathing, three possibly deceased.
Copy. Do we have the shooter in custody?
Shooter is down.
Copy. Shooter down, thank you.
David 4 arriving.
David 4 copy. Can you start setting up blocking roadway to stop entry into the area?
Yes, we need someone at 116.
Copy that. Units will block off at 116.
David 1, I'm going into the area.
Copy. 33 Sam, any units in the area at 108 and Schultz?
33 Sam arriving.
33 Sam copy.
Team setting up.
Roger that. Sam 10, is the scene secure for aid to come in?
Scene secure. Aid can come in.
Copy. Aid has been advised to expedite.
Do you want our team to clear the school?
Yes, set up a team to clear the school from the south side entrance.
Copy that. We're moving in.
Roger. All teams, secure all entrances and exits.
I have a clerk here, room clear.
Copy. 33 Sam, we have additional teams ready to move in.
Sam 10. Five more units coming to the south side.
Copy, five more units on the south side.
Moving 60 from the Adam Charles building.
Roger that. Secure all exits.
We are clearing now.
Copy. Once clear, head to the north side for evacuation.
Command post, have two teams ready.
Copy. Teams are ready and in position.
Command post, one team in the cafeteria.
Copy. One team in the cafeteria.
We have 30 in room PS1.
Copy. Room PS1. Shelter in place.
Eight additional witnesses coming out towards aid units now.
Copy. Eight witnesses to aid units.
Special needs group heading north.
Copy. Special needs group escorted north.
Three deputies have the perimeter on lockdown.
Copy. Perimeter is secure.
David 33-San needs support.
Copy. Additional units are en route to support.
Parents are asking where to pick up their kids.
Parent pick-up at the church on 116 and 51st.
Roger that. Sending parents to the church.
Copy. Transport teams on standby.
Do we have any units checking the surrounding area?
Affirmative, units are checking nearby streets.
Setting up choke points for traffic.
Roger. Choke points in place.
Library is now clear.
Copy. Library clear. Continue clearing other buildings.
